title: count_attachments()
brief: Count the attachments in the current message.
seealso: attachment_colour, save_attachment, attachments, attachment
version: 0.10
----

<p>This function will return an integer count of the number of attachments in the currently specified message.</p>
<p>For example:</p>
<pre>
<a href="/lua/msg.html">msg</a>("There are " .. count_attachments() .. " attachments");
</pre>

